{"tid":1780982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國廈門地鐵驚傳路面坍塌 多輛車輛掉落、泥水灌入站內","createTime":"2019-12-12T22:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T02:55:57.000Z","uid":137672,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"818ad53c4713245ec9e46d76365a09250983656f","tid":1780982,"uid":137672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T22:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymH5n77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymH5n77.jpg&h=3d7ca711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPnXYGs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPnXYGs.jpg&h=c0c134bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕廈門地鐵一號線與二號線的交會站發生路面嚴重坍塌事故，有車輛掉落，中國警方、消防隊已到現場搶救，尚未發現有人員受困。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，12日晚間驚傳廈門地鐵一號線與二號線的交會站「呂厝北站」出現路面坍塌，現場有多輛車輛掉落，根據現在目擊者表示，警消已經抵達現場，目前尚未發現受困人員。<br />\n<br />\n有傳出的影片顯示泥水已經滲出灌進站內，而該路段也已經進入交通管制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3007524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3007524&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8FcwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=76b018e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3007524&h=899735b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3007524</a>"},{"pid":"1d727c3fc4d29c997fa4b6d3dc5a13651c7bf1f9","tid":1780982,"uid":137672,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T22:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pf3Tw4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpf3Tw4c.jpg&h=833be02b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5dbf13b4150cbb9db598ccd1c6f92d6af2d1f39","tid":1780982,"uid":156618,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T22:47:31.000Z","msg":"沙中線嘅未來？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8042c33687862cbacac5c64f68d8ff0d1